cmp::Ordering::is_lt.doc:
Returns `true` if the ordering is the `Less` variant.

# Examples

```
use std::cmp::Ordering;

assert_eq!(Ordering::Less.is_lt(), true);
assert_eq!(Ordering::Equal.is_lt(), false);
assert_eq!(Ordering::Greater.is_lt(), false);
```

